<L>__{interior zoe's bedroom later}
<A>__{the clock by the bed says 2:30 a.m. stan is snoring slightly. nuts is on the pillow beside him. zoe's side is empty.}
<L>__{interior zoe's living room continuous}
<A>__{zoe sits on the floor of the living room sifting through a box of photographs. we follow her back into the bedroom and onto the bed. as stan slowly opens his eyes, she holds up a photograph. his p.o.v. it's a picture of a woman's ass.}
