<P>__{(then)}
<D>__{it also taught me that i should never, under any circumstances, have short hair and a perm again.}
<A>__{she picks up another picture. it's zoe in a bathing cap and speedo. she's holding up a yellow ribbon and has her arm around nana.}
<C>__{zoe }
<D>__{this is one of my favorites because look how happy i am. i don't even know what place yellow is, but i'm sure it's not good.}
